Fieldcrest Cannon Inc said it filedwith the Securities and Exchange Commission a registrationstatement covering a 100 mln dlr issue of convertiblesubordinated debentures.    Proceeds will be used to reduce outstanding bank debt underthe company's revolving credit agreement, Fieldcrest Cannonsaid.    The company named Kidder, Peabody and Co Inc as leadunderwriter of the offering. Reuter&#3;